She embraces her sensuality and dances away her blues; she firmly believes in herself and French Connection United Kingdom accentuates her independence with Connect Her. The luxury fragrance adorns her chic wardrobe and adds an element of completion to her attire as she dresses to paint the town red. The Eau de Toilette not only envelopes her with an aura of unattainability but also leaves her presence lingering in the memories of the ones around.

FCUK Connect Her is a mosaic of aromas that blend together seamlessly to float around you as you move and shake your way through the crowd. The feral scent of jungle pralines headiness of apple martini and carnal tuberose act on the mild notes of almond blossoms and velvety rose petals to create a distinctive aroma. The accords of sandalwood soothe your senses while amber crystals patchouli brandy and the malibu shot get you drunk on their combines potency. Light notes of peach musk tiptoe around in the fragrance spreading its succulence. FCUK Connect Her comes in a distinctive flacon with metal accents and a glass window that reflects the fiery red of the fragrance. Drop the pretense break conventions and forge new paths with FCUK Connect Her made for the modern woman who is unafraid.

Cheeky and fun the woman of today knows how to have her convivial pleasure amidst the serious sombre world. French Connection United Kingdom adorns her with a luxury fragrance that embraces her spirit and cheers her on in her mischievous endeavours. The Eau de Toilette portrays all that she is; a fine balance between cheery fun and sultry sensuousness. Companionable as a friend but unattainable when you want more the FCUK woman is all but a bundle of lovably stark contrasts.

Created in 2004 Geza Schoen captures the modernity of youngsters and makes the fragrance warm and inviting. With a fudgy centre and florals surrounding it FCUK Her turns you into a force of nature that is definitely to be reckoned with. With opening notes of soothing iris which float onto a heart of barringtonia peony violet and jasmine FCUK Her is sensual and subtly provocative. The dry down leaves behind a rich aroma of sandalwood cedar amber and vanilla. Modern and chic the fragrance lures you into its magic and lets you drown in the contemporary bar-like flacon made of glass and metal that encloses it. Indulge the tease in you with FCUK Her EDT.
